Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, do you have anything\Nyou're doing with all your might?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm always in fighting spirits, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Miss Layla is more amazing than I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is always thinking about\Nhow she can improve herself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, it's our show! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll make sure I complete\Nit by all means. I will! I will!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you want to do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time I was asked that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I looked up at the blue sky {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is only in my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't easily say the\Nwords that are really important{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I start running towards\Nthe place the light points to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so much in my heart\Nthat I want to embrace, I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll keep painting my way,\NI promise, take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon,\Nwhere the white clouds drift{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:02:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future is lined up and\Nit'll always be there by my side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I was too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three... One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is less than a week until opening day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is too afraid of missing the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, she becomes nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it makes her miss the timing even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Competition Calls Up A Storm."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what Kalos is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you and she \Nare like oil and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll do anything in order to\Nbe the topic of conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you both just being used by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make the\Nshow somewhat presentable,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're the one who has to adjust to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever his intention is,\Nit's nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three. One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I can't adjust the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I try to watch Miss Layla's moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who has\Nto adjust the timing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Ken to videotape this\Nso I can get a feel for your timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here so I can study\Nyour rhythms and pauses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please try to learn\Nmy moves and rhythms too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your moves and rhythms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought you looked cool\Neven just taking off your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, I give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We eat dinner in the dining hall.\NHow about you, Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the dining hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Miss Layla...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's going to live here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she is going to co-star,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she should have chosen one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, if she chose me, \Nit'd be almost perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind moving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't chosen my stuff yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bowwow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even just walking, Miss Layla looks elegant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I make you coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, I will borrow your shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "shower"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a way to treat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm a little different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even said "Don't worry about it"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negligee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ro... Ro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't think a negligee is a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anyway, please change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rope! Rope! Rope! On the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So, I changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rope! Rope! Gah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please change into this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must follow my rules, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Layla, please use my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Making Miss Layla do something like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can't adjust my timing after this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... I shouldn't think like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to make sure\NI accomplish it by all means.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even her sleeping face is beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little bit different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpected things may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but isn't Miss Layla's\Nvisit here itself something unexpected?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, please don't wake up Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's moves. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's pauses. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's rhythms. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quickly... I have to learn it quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Step in without hesitating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--They still can't get in \Ntune when they have to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's not enough!\N{\i1}--They still can't get in tune when they have to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think those two are\Nstarting to get on the same wavelength?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's trying so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their timing is starting to synchronize.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think they'll be fine in the early scenes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But will they be able to endure\Nthe performance at the climax?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll somehow be\Nable to open on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better if we lower\Nthe difficulty of the climax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you want to\Nmake the climax scene easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, let's get rid\Nof the idea of using the diabolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Co-starring with a newcomer\Nis enough adventure in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a director,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to avoid any more adventures\Nthan what we're doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I worked hard for--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to make the climax easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us tomorrow, one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the Generalprobe,\Nthe dress rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already postponed until\Ntomorrow just for the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will use substitutes for the Generalprobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she had some phone calls to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,\Nwe get one more day, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you will do fine, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. How is everything going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We somehow managed to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the weather\Nalso started cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The weather started cooperating"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our timing was finally beginning to match...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be okay to practice \Nover the real sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget everything we\Nhave done up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also been working so hard,\Njust trying to adjust the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how many times I repeat\Nthe same things like I've been doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the final product will\Nbe a safe and boring show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real fight between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A real fight with Miss Layla? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will you accept this challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want a lifeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will get in my way when I move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't need it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beginning to look like a real enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has such amazing spirit. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I lose my nerve even a little,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she really is going to knock me in the sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drop your guard, you'll be shark bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over the real sea, no one can\Npredict the movement of the waves,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}not even Miss Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to be doing special training\Nin the middle of the sea around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the rehearsal, please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show will open as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah, it's not your turn yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I did it. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Keep an eye on the\Nspace in the front and the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick! I think you should step\Nforward there, and let's try an ad-lib.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cruising?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening day is tomorrow.\NI wonder if they'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume Miss Layla has something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm worried about the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you reaching your limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with all the noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you guys keep\Nstanding there, it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really make tomorrow's opening date?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the seas in the direction\Nof the port are still rough,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will drop anchor here until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, tomorrow is finally a real show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a real show...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they could have\Nrain in a real performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're truly amazing, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always thinking about Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, why did you join Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Kaleido Stage with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so wonderful. Like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the show was wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought it was strange\Nto see my mother and father
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,laughing and being\Nsurprised as if they were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which show was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alice's Adventures in Wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alice's Adventures in Wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show I saw with my parents was\Nalso Alice's Adventures in Wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, of course, it became the last\Nmemory that I had with both my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my first and last time seeing my\Nmother surprised and laughing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After my mother died,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my father devoted himself to work \Nto take his mind off of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if your father\Ncould see you onstage this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Did I say something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never told this to anybody before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This girl may possess a power\Nthat can change her surroundings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, the audience\Nwill come here just to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you talk a lot in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking in my sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she talking about the\Ntime when I was talking to Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming back today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to stay overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They never told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something unexpected happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait one more night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, please come back by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will start opening day as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla and Sora are heading here directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be here very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. They made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have you back. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean, I want you to prepare rain for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's faster than yesterday. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Five seconds before flame ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Ignite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames ignite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not received this kind of\Npleasant applause for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy and I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, what do you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never say you don't get any of that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sleep, play, flip through a magazine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, you're lonely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like always, invisible vibes fly\Naround the city today, tulututu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, the vector of my heart\Nis talking about so many reasons{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be free and fly the skies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't have space to spread my wings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have faith {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a future yet to be shaped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there's a me that I want to shape{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I'm sad, even if it's a mistake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do what I want and\Nfly towards the freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not so easy that you'll get\Napplause for just following the script.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I alone have to\Nwork even though it's my day off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moreover, she is going to appear on stage\Nas a guest for another theatrical company.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm coming with you. So, hold on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Going through ordeals in a\Ncompletely different environment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Out of the frying pan into\Nthe fire. Into the fire! Into the fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:23:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"Mysterious Amazing Circus."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:24:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on toward the sky...{\i0}
